cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with vehicle detection in aerial and satellite images using deep learning techniques. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes the use of recent work on deep learning for wide-area motion imagery (WAMI) on satellite video. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with the use of AI techniques for vehicle detection in satellite video. 
4. cs.RO (Robotics) is a possible category as the paper deals with object detection in remote sensing imagery, which is relevant to robotics applications. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with vehicle detection in satellite video, which is a form of multimedia data.
